data.oai_dc:dc: The paired-end deep-sequence data from this paper was generated as a single lane of Illumina data, but was split up into 6 parts (A-F) for Dryad submission. This is part D. The file will unzip into two files containing the paired-end reads for the fourth 5.5M sequenced clusters. Phred+64 quality score encoding. Library prep details can be found in the Methods of the linked manuscript.
